DESCRIPTION:Join us for an inside look at our graduate programs and discov
 er how IU SPH-B is designed to support your success both in and out of th
 e classroom. You’ll learn about academic advising\, career services\, stu
 dent organizations\, and the wide range of student support resources avai
 lable to you. We’ll also highlight IU spirit and traditions\, the vibrant
  student life experience\, and the many advantages of living in Bloomingt
 on\, Indiana. The session will conclude with a live Q&A\, offering you th
 e chance to connect directly with our admissions team. No matter where yo
 u are in the application process\, this session is a great opportunity to
  learn how IU SPH-B can support your academic journey and help prepare yo
 u for a rewarding and impactful career in public health. \nRegister Here!
 \nQuestions? Schedule a time to chat or email sphgrad@iu.edu\n\nHosted by
 : Graduate Engagement\, Admissions\, and Recruitment at IU School of Publ
 ic Health-Bloomington\n\nOnline Location: https://iuusssad-fireform.eas.i
 u.edu/online/form/index/BLMPHInfoSessio\n\nAdditional Information can be 
 found at: https://beinvolved.indiana.edu/event/12161457
