DESCRIPTION:Come spend your Thursdays at the ACC practicing your Tagalog a
 nd celebrating Filipino culture! Every Thursday from 4:00-5:00 PM\, we’ll
  host a variety of language-immersive events—(included but not limited to
 ) language table\, speech practice\, Tagalog tutoring\, cooking workshops
 —to introduce the aspects that Filipino culture has to offer. Tagalog na 
 Tayo! is open to everyone\, whether you’re a beginner\, fluent speaker\, 
 or simply curious about Filipino culture.  \nAll Indiana University event
 s\, groups\, activities\, and educational\, cultural\, and historical obs
