DESCRIPTION:Description: The term Mehendi is the Indian word for Henna\, a
 nd it is also the term used to describe the art of applying henna. Come a
 nd learn the basic designs and application techniques of Henna or Mehendi
 \, which is used to create temporary tattoos. Please feel free to bring y
 our friends to learn more about Desi culture and the significance of Mehe
 ndi in the Indian culture! If you come with a group of more than 7 member
 s\, please email acc@iu.edu in advance so we can prepare the henna materi
 als.   \n \n\nHosted by: Asian Culture Center\n\nAdditional Information c
 an be found at: https://beinvolved.indiana.edu/event/11988304
DTEND:20260327T210000Z
