DESCRIPTION:Join us for the Student Involvement and Leadership Center's Le
 adership Compass Series\, a monthly leadership development series designe
 d to help students grow across the 8 Student Leadership Competency domain
 s. Each session will focus on one core leadership area—ranging from self-
 awareness to civic responsibility—through interactive workshops and hands
 -on activities. This 8-workshop series (spanning the academic year) provi
 des a dynamic space for students to build confidence\, sharpen their skil
 ls\, and connect with peers who are passionate about personal and communi
 ty growth.\nWhether you're new to leadership or already involved on campu
 s\, the SILC Leadership Compass offers practical tools and meaningful con
 versations to elevate your leadership journey—one domain at a time.\n \n*
 **Lunch is provided for participants from 12:00pm-1:00pm on all dates***\
 n \n<!--StartFragment -->\n📅 March 28th\, 2026⏰ 10:00 AM – 3:00 PM📍 IMU
  Club Hub\n💡 Teams thrive when dynamics are intentional—but how do leade
 rs foster collaboration and navigate challenges effectively? In "Group Dy
 namics\," the next event in the Leadership Compass Series\, we’ll explore
  the Group Dynamics domain of the Student Leadership Competencies\, equip
 ping you with the tools 🔄 to build trust\, enhance teamwork\, and lead g
 roups through both strengths and struggles with confidence.\n🔥 Great tea
 ms don’t just work together—they grow together. Let’s refine how you lead
  and support your team!\nAll Indiana University events\, groups\, activit
 ies\, and educational\, cultural\, and historical observances welcome all
  IU students and other members of the Indiana University community.\n<!--
 EndFragment -->\n\nHosted by: Student Involvement and Leadership Center\n
 \nAdditional Information can be found at: https://beinvolved.indiana.edu/
 event/11321023
DTEND:20260328T190000Z
DTSTAMP:20260309T020709Z
DTSTART:20260328T140000Z
LOCATION:IMU Club Hub
SEQUENCE:0
STATUS:CONFIRMED
SUMMARY:SILC Leadership Compass Series - "Group Dynamics"
UID:https://beinvolved.indiana.edu/event/11321023
URL:https://beinvolved.indiana.edu/event/11321023
X-HOSTS:Student Involvement and Leadership Center
END:VEVENT
