DESCRIPTION:Live Reality Games @ IU brings the hit game show The Floor to 
 campus! 🧠🔥\nStep onto the floor and put your knowledge to the test in a
  fast-paced\, competitive trivia experience where every square counts. Pa
 rticipants will face off in head-to-head challenges across a variety of c
 ategories\, battling to claim territory and outlast the competition.\nWit
 h over $200 in prizes on the line\, the stakes are high and the energy is
  even higher. Whether you’re a trivia master or just in it for the fun\, 
 The Floor @ IU is your chance to compete\, win\, and show what you’ve got
