DESCRIPTION:Join Truth Advance - Men's Bible Study at Indiana University\,
  for a recurring gathering focused on exploring scripture and fostering p
 ersonal growth. Expect a structured yet open environment where participan
 ts study the Bible\, share perspectives\, and build connections through f
 ellowship. Whether you're deepening your faith or simply curious\, this i
