DESCRIPTION:\nAll students are welcome to join Ski and Snowboard Club at I
 U at any point in the year\, no previous ski or ride experience necessary
 ! Our weekly committee meetings are a fun way to meet other club members 
 and the students on the executive committee while learning about all our 
 year round events and activities - social events\, co-ed intramural sport
 s\, Polar Plunge for Special Olympics\, supporting SKI women’s Little 500
  cycling team\, local ski/ride at Perfect North Slopes\, and trips during
  winter and spring break to real mountains!\n \n\nour website --> https:/
 /www.skiandboardatiu.com/ \ninstagram --> @skiandboardatiu\n\nHosted by: 
 Ski and Snowboard Club at Indiana University\n\nAdditional Information ca
 n be found at: https://beinvolved.indiana.edu/event/12233953
