DESCRIPTION:OverviewBlack in Business is partnering with the American Red 
 Cross to host a campus wide blood drive focused on increasing representat
 ion from minority student organizations and expanding access to life savi
 ng donations. This event will take place in February or March. The exact 
 date and location are still being confirmed. We will secure the location 
 from 12 to 8\, and the active donation window will run from 3 to 7. There
  is also interest in making this a multi day drive to maximize impact.\nE
 vent Purpose• Promote equitable access to blood donation• Mobilize minori
 ty led organizations across IU• Strengthen collaboration between Black in
  Business and campus partners• Deliver a high impact service project cent
 ered on community well being\n\nHosted by: Black in Business\n\nAdditiona
 l Information can be found at: https://beinvolved.indiana.edu/event/12247
