 \, with riveting conversation and maybe food. We'll see. \nWhether you're
  only watching because you think Colby is hot\, or you're excited to see 
 Cirie lose for the eighth time\, our event is open to Survivor fans new a
 nd old! Great way to meet fun people and a good hang on a Wednesday night
 .\n\nHosted by: Live Reality Games @ IU\n\nAdditional Information can be 
 found at: https://beinvolved.indiana.edu/event/12120731
